    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to a doc but i honestly dont have the time or the money for another appointment right now lol. it's just a supplement anyway, right? like it's not like it's a heavy chemical. if i just slowly lower my dose of sertraline over a week while i start taking the st johns wort, wouldnt that make the transition pretty smooth? i just want to get off the synthetic stuff.",
